 games are slated for 7 am. Also the game between Rima Strikers and Plateau Vipers (M). COAS Shooters lock horns with Borno Spiders (M), Edo Dynamos battle Safety Babes (F ), while Kada Stars and Lagos Seasiders (Male) fight for the two points at stake. Vanguard Imo Grasshoppers yesterday proved why they are famous handball team in the country as they defeated eastern rival, Abia Valiants 32-15 to remain unbeaten in the concluding phase of the Prudent Energy Handball League taking place at the Mobolaji Johnson Sports Complex, Rowe Park, Yaba. September 28, 2018 In "News" Imo Grasshoppers yesterday proved why they are famous handball team in the country as they defeated eastern rival, Abia Valiants 32-15 to remain unbeaten in the concluding phase of the Prudent Energy Handball League taking place at the Mobolaji Johnson Sports Complex, Rowe Park, Yaba. October 1, 2018 In "Sports" Kano Pillars Handball Club became the first team to record a win after beating Lagos Seasiders 38-27 in the opening game of the Prudent Energy Handball league, which began yesterday at the sports hall of the National Stadium in Abuja. May 15, 2019 In "News"